<div id='communityQuestionsWithAnswers'>
<div class='communityQuestionAndAnswer'>
<div class='communityQuestion'>
<div class='questionText'>
<a href="/questions/1584940-free-thought-and-expression-of-ideas-are">Free thought and expression of ideas are essential for human development. By reading the story of Boethius we understand the hardships of the free thinkers in the ways of the past and the agony and end of the enlightened ones who passed from the world but in memories of generations through their thoughtful insights and writing. How he accomplished the writing in the jail seems to be a mystery and question.?</a>
</div>
<div class='communityQAFooter questionFooter'>
<ul class='questionFooterActions'>
<li class='footerItem like'>
<span class='likeItContainer' id='like_container_community_question_1584940'><a id="like_count_community_question_1584940" rel="nofollow" href="/rating/voters/1584940?resource_type=CommunityQuestion"><span class="likesCount">1 like</span></a>&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;<a rel="nofollow" class="jsLike like_it" href="https://www.goodreads.com/user/new?remember=true&amp;return_url=%2Fbook%2Fshow%2F31837.The_Consolation_of_Philosophy">like</a></span>

</li>
<li class='footerItem communityQuestionTimestamp'>
